<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>회원가입</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Apple Style Custom CSS */
        :root {
            --apple-bg: #f5f5f7;
            --apple-blue: #0071e3;
            --apple-blue-hover: #0077ed;
            --apple-text: #1d1d1f;
            --apple-gray: #86868b;
        }
        body {
            background-color: var(--apple-bg);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--apple-text);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Minimal Header */
        .simple-header {
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .simple-header a {
            color: var(--apple-text);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .simple-header a:hover { color: var(--apple-blue); }

        /* Login Card */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .auth-card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        .auth-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .auth-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--apple-gray);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Inputs */
        .form-control {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
            background-color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--apple-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(0, 113, 227, 0.2);
        }

        /* Button */
        .btn-apple {
            background-color: var(--apple-blue);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            width: 100%;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-apple:hover {
            background-color: var(--apple-blue-hover);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .simple-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--apple-gray);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="simple-header">
    <nav>
        <a href="/main">Home</a>
        <a href="/user/login">Login</a>
        <a href="/user/join" style="color: var(--apple-blue);">Join</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<div class="main-content">
    <div class="auth-card">
        <h1 class="auth-title">계정 생성</h1>
        <p class="auth-subtitle">서비스 이용을 위해 계정을 만들어주세요.</p>

        {{#errorMessage}}
            <div class="alert alert-danger text-center p-2 mb-4" style="font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px;">
                {{errorMessage}}
            </div>
        {{/errorMessage}}

        <form action="/user/join" method="post">

            <div class="mb-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="username" placeholder="아이디" required>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="nickname" name="nickname" placeholder="닉네임" required>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-apple">계정 만들기</button>

            <div class="mt-4 text-center">
                <span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-gray);">이미 계정이 있으신가요?</span>
                <a href="/user/login" style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-blue); text-decoration: none; margin-left: 5px;">로그인하기 ↗</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="simple-footer">
    Copyright © 2026. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>